{
  "title": "Smoky Roasted Ethiopian Teff Stir-fry",
  "description": "A quick-fix ethiopian dish featuring ketchup for a bitter and gooey texture, with a touch of smoke to make it dash-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Ethiopian",
  "diet": [
